Basic game and shot clock application for using on laptop, displayed towards
the players and referees.

No scoreboard or foul registration included because of limited screen sizes.


Quick help in title bar, most important keyboard keys:
* <Space> : start stop game clock
* <Enter> : reset 24 second shot clock
* f : reset to 14 second shot clock

Alternative control via mouse buttons to reset shot clocks:
* left : 24 seconds
* right : 14 seconds

BEWARE: 14 seconds only available when game clock is STOPPED.